                    </audio>
                    <p class="smallertext"><i>Translation: Are you free this Sunday?</i></p>
                </div><br />
            </li>

            <li>
                <h5 id="remun/milikinContent">Remun/Milikin</h5>
                <p>
                    Remun dialect is quite different compare to the other Iban dialects.
                    Most Iban people who speaks Remun also speaks Bidayuh Bukar-Sadong,
                    which may be considered more difficult than the standard Bidayuh.
                </p>
