                        <source src="~/audio/Chinese_Cantonese_Are-you-full.mp3" type="audio/mp3" />
                    </audio>
                    <p class="smallertext"><i>Translation: Are you full?</i></p>
                </div><br />
            </li>

            <li>
                <h5 id="hokkienContent">Hokkien</h5>
                <p>
                    Hokkien, also known as Bân-lâm-ōe amongst many others, is a Southern Min language originating from
                    the Minnan region of the southeastern part of Fujian province in Southeastern Mainlain China. Other
                    than its widely usage in Sarawak and other Malaysian states, it is also widely spoken in Taiwan.
                </p>
                <br />
                <div class=" audioBorder">
